{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"StyleSheet","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/disabled\"><code>disabled</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/href\"><code>href</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/media\"><code>media</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/ownerNode\"><code>ownerNode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/parentStyleSheet\"><code>parentStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/title\"><code>title</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/type\"><code>type</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>CSSOM に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><span class=\"diff_add\"></span></div>\n\n<p><code>StyleSheet</code>インターフェースを実装するオブジェクトは、単一のスタイルシートを表します。CCSスタイルシートは、より特殊化された<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a>インターフェースを実装します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"disabled\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/disabled\" title=\"disabled\"><code>disabled</code></a></dt>\n <dd>このプロパティは、現在のスタイルシートが適用されているかどうかを示します。</dd>\n <dt id=\"href\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/href\" title=\"href\"><code>href</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>スタイルシートの位置を返します。</dd>\n <dt id=\"media\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/media\" title=\"media\"><code>media</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>Specifies the intended destination medium for style information.</dd>\n <dt id=\"ownernode\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/ownerNode\" title=\"ownerNode\"><code>ownerNode</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>このスタイルシートをドキュメントに関連付けるノードを返します。</dd>\n <dt id=\"parentstylesheet\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/parentStyleSheet\" title=\"parentStyleSheet\"><code>parentStyleSheet</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>存在する場合、これを含む&nbsp;<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a> を返します; ない場合は&nbsp;<code>null</code>&nbsp;を返します。</dd>\n <dt id=\"title\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/title\" title=\"title\"><code>title</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>現在のスタイルシートへのアドバイザリタイトルを表す&nbsp;<a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> を返します。</dd>\n <dt id=\"type\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/type\" title=\"type\"><code>type</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>このスタイルシートのスタイルシート言語を表す&nbsp;<a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> を返します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">策定状況</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#stylesheet\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)<br><small lang=\"ja\">StyleSheet の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specificationの仕様書\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification</a> から変更なし</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/stylesheets.html#StyleSheets-StyleSheet\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification<br><small lang=\"ja\">StyleSheet の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">廃止</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザー実装状況","id":"ブラウザー実装状況","isH3":false,"query":"api.StyleSheet","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specification"},{"text":"ブラウザー実装状況","id":"ブラウザー実装状況"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"StyleSheetインターフェースを実装するオブジェクトは、単一のスタイルシートを表します。CCSスタイルシートは、より特殊化されたCSSStyleSheetインターフェースを実装します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"StyleSheet","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"objeto Stylesheet","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"StyleSheet","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"StyleSheet","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"StyleSheet","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"StyleSheet","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/stylesheet","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/stylesheet/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet","title":"StyleSheet"}],"pageTitle":"StyleSheet - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}